description: Using existing Modern Rock 500 lists (all years 1989-2009, except for 1994, 1998, and 2004), point totals assigned as such: #1 = 500, #2  = 499, #500 = 1. Results tabulated to find the Modern Rock 500's top 500! A few songs are missing.
name: 97x Modern Rock 500 - Top 500 1989-2009
